(72, 5, 13, '<p xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>Tujuh tahun yang lalu, umur ayah sama dengan enam kali umur Kleo. Jika tahun depan umur ayah 2 lebihnya dari tiga kali umur Kleo, berapa tahun umur Kleo lima tahun yang akan datang?</span></span></span></p>', '<p>13</p>', '<p>15</p>', '<p>17</p>', '<p>18</p>', '<p>19</p>', 4, '<ol>\r\n <li xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>A – 7 = 6 (K – 7) </span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>A – 7 = 6K – 42 </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>A = 6K – 35 </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed> </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n <li xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>A + 1 = 3(K + 1) + 2 </span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>A + 1 = 3K + 3 + 2  </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>A = 3K + 4 </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed> </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n <li xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>3K + 4 = 6B – 35 </span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>3K = 39 </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>K = 13 </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>Jadi umur Kleo lima tahun yang akan datang adalah K + 5 = 18 </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>', '2020-12-07 19:40:58', '2020-12-07 19:40:58'),
(73, 6, 4, '<p>Perhatikan reaksi termokimia berikut:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>C(grafit) + O<sub>2</sub>(g) → CO<sub>2</sub>(g)    ∆H = - 432 Kj/mol</p>\r\n\r\n<p>CaO(s) + CO<sub>2</sub>(g)  →  CaCO<sub>3</sub>(s) ∆H = - 180 Kj/mol</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Apabila panas yang dihasilkan dari pembakaran grafit digunakan untuk membuat CaO dari CaCO<sub>3</sub>, maka massa grafit yang dibutuhkan untuk menghasilkan 5,6 Kg CaO adalah….</p>', '<p>0,25 Kg</p>', '<p>0,50 Kg</p>', '<p>1,80 Kg</p>', '<p>2,00 Kg</p>', '<p>4,00 Kg</p>', 2, '<p>C(grafit) + O<sub>2</sub>(g)  →  CO<sub>2</sub>(g)       ∆H = - 432 Kj/mol</p>\r\n\r\n<p>CaO(s) + CO<sub>2</sub>(g) →  CaCO<sub>3</sub>(s) ∆H = - 180 Kj/mol (dibalik)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mol CaO = 5600/56 = 100 mol</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Energi untuk menghasilkan 100 mol CaO = 100 x (+180) = 18000 Kj (berasal dari pembakaran grafit/C)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>∆H = Q/mol </p>\r\n\r\n<p>432   = 18000/mol; mol = 41,67 mol</p>\r\n\r\n<p>massa C = 41,67 x 12 = 500 gram = <strong>0,5 Kg</strong></p>', '2020-12-07 19:42:14', '2020-12-07 19:42:46'),
(74, 5, 13, '<p><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>Asep mengendarai mobil ke kantornya selama 1 jam dengan jarak 30 km. Jika dia terlambat berangkat 20 menit, kecepatan yang harus digunakan agar sampai ke kantor adalah …</span></span></span></p>', '<p><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>37 km/jam</span></span></span></p>', '<p><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>40 km/jam</span></span></span></p>', '<p><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>42 km/jam</span></span></span></p>', '<p><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>43 km/jam</span></span></span></p>', '<p><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>45 km/jam</span></span></span></p>', 5, '<p><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><img src=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/Sj_jfl2vrVtEMQ-KUzdseJ6zT0J4peqozwboPopYobltcSD-YWXjAHIKpehCHZ22ZawF5SeQy--9lPqysqo_Kk5PmHtgQuQAiQAAPRIGY-e1z6Hdj3zlMba6s7p0ik--rXbEixI\" xss=removed></span></span></span></p>', '2020-12-07 19:42:16', '2020-12-07 19:42:16'),
(75, 4, 12, '<p>The virus causing illness in Wuhan is a novel coronavirus &ndash; a member of the coronavirus family that has never been encountered before. Like other coronaviruses, it is zoonotic, meaning it is transmitted between animals and people. New and troubling viruses usually originate in animal hosts. Severe Acute Respiratory Syndrome (SARS) and Middle Eastern Respiratory Syndrome (MERS) are both caused by coronaviruses that came from animals. Although MERS is believed to be transmitted to humans from dromedaries (Arabian camels), the original hosts for both coronaviruses were probably bats.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Wuhan novel coronavirus causes pneumonia. Those who have fallen ill are reported to suffer coughs, fever and breathing difficulties. In severe cases there can be organ failure. As this is viral pneumonia, antibiotics are of no use. The antiviral drugs we have against flu will not work. If people are admitted to hospital, they may get support for their lungs and other organs as well as fluids. Recovery will depend on the strength of their immune system. Many of those who have died were already in poor health.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Human to human transmission has been confirmed by China&rsquo;s national health commission. Many of those infected either worked or frequently shopped in the Huanan seafood wholesale market in the centre of the Chinese city, which also sold live and newly slaughtered animals. As of 30 January, the death toll in China stands at 170, with more than 7,500 confirmed cases of infections. In the past week, the number of confirmed infections has more than tripled and cases have been found in 13 provinces, as well as the municipalities of Beijing, Shanghai, Chongqing and Tianjin. The virus has been confirmed outside mainland China, in Hong Kong, Macau, Taiwan, and in Japan, Nepal, Singapore, South Korea, Thailand, the US, and Vietnam. Two members of one family have been confirmed to have the virus in the UK, after more than 160 were tested and found negative. The actual number to have contracted the virus could be far higher as people with mild symptoms may not have been detected. Modelling by World Health Organization (WHO) experts at Imperial College London suggests there could be as many as 100,000 cases, with uncertainty putting the margins between 30,000 and 200,000.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>(Adapted from https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/jan/31/what-is-coronavirus-symptoms-wuhan-china-how-worried-doctor)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>15.&nbsp;It can be concluded from the passage that &hellip;</p>', '<p>the animal hosts of Wuhan novel coronavirus and the other members of the virus are believed coming from the same animals</p>', '<p>MERS, SARS, and Wuhan illness are caused by the coronavirus family which is transmitted between animals and people</p>', '<p>Wuhan novel coronavirus has the same effect as SARS that it causes suffer coughs, fever, and breathing difficulties</p>', '<p>the China&rsquo;s national health commission has confirmed that the virus is transmitted from human to human</p>', '<p>antibiotics and flu antiviral drugs are not effective in encountering the Wuhan novel coronavirus</p>', 2, '<p>Simpulan dari bacaan adalah bahwa penyebab penyakit MERS, SARS, dan yang sedang merebak di Wuhan adalah keluarga coronavirus yang ditularkan dari hewan ke manusia. Hal ini sejalan dengan gagasan utama bacaan.</p>', '2020-12-07 19:43:29', '2020-12-10 02:30:40'),
(76, 5, 13, '<p xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>Seorang pekerja mengecat tembok yang tingginya 3 m dan telah sepertiganya selesai. Jika selanjutnya dia mengecat tembok 5 m persegi lagi, dia telah akan selesai mengecat </span></span></span><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><img src=\"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/7K82bZFFrvyyfig0rut_gMHTpUi0OUFkRDugXlUdH5uqvucWqpjdzDGudYFmOHzcHZyGyjMohef-8YsvgHWk-4B-fNEkSdVr3vv8o23-cUshhWacLVSFa3kQ1XOu3XQMYC-f3ss\" xss=removed></span></span></span><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed> luas tembok. Berapakah panjang tembok itu?</span></span></span></p>', '<p><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>4 meter</span></span></span></p>', '<p><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>5 meter</span></span></span></p>', '<p><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>6 meter</span></span></span></p>', '<p><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>7 meter</span></span></span></p>', '<p><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>8 meter</span></span></span></p>', 1, '<p><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/IgHLbJyqprI5Aii0-w-aKCFZiBkGtEr08VXG2kbF5hlGLq6moKmL3ZPd1klMOkq5HWXBJzh5LyaUiN9jk98XZdRvoFTK_-qPBRZAAyLmJ6nIjiUUrv_4uK4ZSN5Jvq3OcONuOww\" xss=removed></span></span></span></p>', '2020-12-07 19:43:35', '2020-12-07 19:43:35'),
(77, 6, 4, '<p>Molekul H<sub>2</sub>NCH<sub>2</sub>COOH tidak dapat membentuk polimer.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>SEBAB</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Reaksi antara gugus karboksilat (−COOH) dengan gugus amino (−NH<sub>2</sub>) antar dua molekul H<sub>2</sub>NCH<sub>2</sub>CH<sub>2</sub>COOH merupakan reaksi kondensasi.</p>', '<p>Bila pernyataan benar, alasan benar, dan keduanya menunjukan sebab akibat</p>', '<p>Bila pernyataan benar, alasan benar, tetapi keduanya tidak menunjukan sebab akibat</p>', '<p>Bila pernyataan benar, dan alasan salah</p>', '<p>Bila pernyataan salah, dan alasan benar</p>', '<p>Bila pernyataan dan alasan salah</p>', 4, '<p>Molekul H<sub>2</sub>NCH<sub>2</sub>COOH merupakan asam amino <strong>pembentuk polimer protein</strong>. Pembentukan protein melalui reaksi <strong>kondensasi </strong>dengan melepas molekul H<sub>2</sub>O.</p>', '2020-12-07 19:44:06', '2020-12-07 19:58:14'),
(78, 3, 11, '<p>(1) Survei berjudul &quot;International Public Opinion Survey on Cancer 2020: What people feel, think, and believe about cancer today&quot; yang dilakukan oleh Union for International Cancer Control (UICC) menunjukkan perbedaan yang jelas antara masyarakat kelompok ekonomi tinggi dan rendah dalam hal pengetahuan dan kesadaran akan faktor resiko kanker. (2) Survei ini dilakukan terhadap 15.472 orang dewasa di 20 negara untuk peringatan Hari Kanker Sedunia ke-20.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>(3) Hasil survei menunjukkan, masyarakat kelas ekonomi menengah ke atas ditemukan memiliki kesadaran dan pemahaman yang lebih tinggi tentang kanker dibandingkan masyarakat kelas ekonomi menengah ke bawah. (4) Selain itu, hasil survei ini menemukan beberapa faktor resiko yang paling &#39;populer&#39; di tengah masyarakat. (5) Kebiasaan merokok (63%), paparan sinar ultraviolet (54%), dan paparan asap rokok dari orang lain (50%) merupakan tiga faktor resiko yang paling dikenali dan disadari. (6) ... faktor resiko seperti kurang aktivitas fisik atau olahraga (28%), paparan virus atau bakteri tertentu (28%), dan kelebihan berat badan (29%) menjadi yang paling tidak &#39;populer&#39; di tengah masyarakat.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>(7) Masyarakat dari golongan rumah tangga berpendapatan rendah ditemukan lebih tidak mengenali faktor resiko kanker daripada mereka yang berasal dari rumah tangga berpendapatan tinggi. (8) Tren ini juga ditemukan terjadi di antara orang dengan tingkat pendidikan tinggi (setara universitas) dengan yang rendah. (9) Sementara beberapa mengaku memahami faktor resiko kanker, beberapa lainnya justru mengaku sama sekali tak tahu-menahu. (10) Dalam kategori ini, masyarakat dengan pendapatan rendah menjadi kelompok terbesar (9%), diikuti oleh masyarakat menengah (6%), dan masyarakat menengah ke atas (4%). (11) Selain kurang mengenali faktor resiko, mereka dengan pendidikan dan tingkat ekonomi rendah juga ditemukan tidak proaktif dalam mengambil langkah-langkah demi mengurangi resiko kanker.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>(12) Dari hasil survei ini, UICC menyerukan agar pemerintah setiap negara dapat memprioritaskan peningkatan kesadaran masyarakat terhadap kanker melalui kebijakan dan pendidikan kesehatan yang progresif. (13) Pemerintah juga diminta fokus pada kelompok masyarakat kelas menengah ke bawah. (14) Selain itu, pemerintah juga diminta untuk menerapkan kebijakan demi mengurangi konsumsi produk penyebab kanker seperti tembakau serta makanan dan minuman bergula.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>(Diadaptasi dari https://www.cnnindonesia.com/gaya-hidup/20200204112310-255-471434/survei-masyarakat-menengah-bawah-tak-sadar-resiko-kanker)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kata &ldquo;mereka&rdquo; pada kalimat (11) mengacu pada .....</p>', '<p>masyarakat di 20 negara</p>', '<p>masyarakat berpendidikan rendah</p>', '<p>masyarakat berpenghasilan rendah</p>', '<p>masyarakat yang menjadi koresponden survei</p>', '<p>masyarakat berpendidikan dan berpenghasilan rendah</p>', 4, '<p>Kunci Jawabannya adalah <strong>(D)</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Pembahasan</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kata mereka pada kalimat (11) mengacu pada masyarakat yang menjadi koresponden survei (yaitu 15.472 orang dewasa di 20 negara).</p>', '2020-12-07 19:44:20', '2020-12-10 02:34:44'),
(79, 5, 13, '<p xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>Dua mobil menuju kota yang berjarak 450 km. Kecepatan mobil kedua 15 km/jam lebih cepat daripada mobil pertama. Jika waktu perjalanan mobil kedua lebih singkat dari waktu perjalanan mobil pertama, berapa km/jam kecepatan yang dipacu mobil pertama?</span></span></span></p>', '<p>80</p>', '<p>90</p>', '<p>95</p>', '<p>75</p>', '<p>105</p>', 4, '<p><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><img src=\"https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/39-go0_ElCK5E-vqyxUKY_dGXaY_baLiz7GEpTaYpPT8MezmCKJTK9amKjmPzMnaC-KHsO0rylpZVpbSfonSKMitg0SPK6ht_JF7PflW6a7zDHX6gutSDAHlnPCFzX83eBIp0qY\" xss=removed></span></span></span></p>', '2020-12-07 19:45:08', '2020-12-07 19:45:08'),
