(132, 7, 1, '<p>Suku banyak f(x) = (a+1)x<sup>3</sup> &ndash; 3bx<sup>2</sup> + 9x turunan keduanya habis dibagi oleh ( x- 1). Jika f(x) tidak mempunyai ektrem lokal maka nilai b adalah....</p>', '<p>-1</p>', '<p>-2</p>', '<p>0</p>', '<p>1&nbsp;</p>', '<p>2</p>', 3, '<p>Suku banyak f(x) = (a+1)x<sup>3</sup> &ndash; 3bx<sup>2</sup> + 9x turunan keduanya habis dibagi oleh ( x- 1). Jika f(x) tidak mempunyai ektrem lokal maka nilai b adalah....</p>\r\n\r\n<p>F&rdquo;(x) = 6(a+1)x &ndash; 6b habis dibagi oleh (x &ndash; 1)&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>F&rdquo;(1) = 0</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/qD4vf6NV0EsdG-PmBpJLhgf_i33s9dQDrwSKyA6XKYqD4lakXGVLsyKTKtkSwQesDf1IEztwfOKov7bczPOZ1IFkaGDYJ4kct0OFUU9GEyAtEahUO2c2gnTyqmJ-rm6Snk1IsOY\" />&nbsp;6(a+1) &ndash; 6b = 0</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/rBngAOk-AB529hEiVWpXEkrnqyOtAsHWwZ1jhUvxeF1BBHNu6D8jEprPuWERXGtxDkyGoGfdZxTfvhDd7NAEnsTqBY70e8ic8NFkta1S2VUa3LustqeQkcK4E-V9GC2dKNQ6pR0\" />&nbsp;a+1 &ndash; b = 0</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/MPWH0M6pnbIwIRgT8RftuEhHPQxDoAJkhsrNtSl-P2nWUELUHMsQIA6gxNNQRAyPgHYLUbvuwoPbjrvGJobTQ3rPA4QH2GNr52pcg2Ca5hvun0np1NPRWdcGFOGiWNEj1HyCQqQ\" />&nbsp;a = b &ndash; 1 ......(1)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/PiwAJpOgWgJjaBkTWwrX54cnMyl13gZ5djiql3ilExi_jERZyRiD4cpBZIfPxqslZKQEFLQ2FSZjPbVat7-UbVfT_ffomTk33aIsCqaC0pDDicfWXHA_qz2HaXh7T3FTbFDx9Lc\" />(x) tidak mempunyai ekstrem : f&rsquo;(x) &lt; 0&gt; 0</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/nwiyqz-C5JxhgzMic-4O9ExGv-v4wUWYooadfCzkBodxPCzjMYfZsafIk4QUNsnMZL6qd4rRUg3nJ6XVZps3CSpX4eA8amNKkDcwd_E5D_m32LOAnNJhDSadZgjcMJiNJC1ks1Q\" />&rsquo;(x) = 3(a+1)x<sup>2</sup> &ndash; 6bx + 9 &lt; 0&gt;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/z8h44CxS_KbrAlKfKGJCuR8DVyAQfTPsohuEp04m9U4g0avylMl93vM5GKhfoqJxNJu8Gro5iaK_WtoR2443cJvyaxemjTgDV2rwd4yc2p7qyKZQtC77JlJz5P2HMmuyNojzr2U\" /> 3bx<sup>2</sup> 6 bx + 9 &lt; 0&gt;</p>\r\n\r\